<div class="py-4">
    <p class="text-secondary mb-4" style="font-size: 1.1rem;">Licensing requirements and application instructions for motor vehicle salespersons and finance/insurance personnel in West Virginia.</p>
    <hr class="mb-4" style="border-color: #cfd8e3;" />

    <p class="section-label">Instructions &amp; Reminders</p>
    <div class="reminder-panel mb-4">
        <ul>
            <li>Salespersons and Finance/Insurance personnel <strong>must</strong> be licensed. The salesperson license must be kept in his/her possession at all times.</li>
            <li>Renewal fee for a salesperson license is <strong>$10.00</strong>.</li>
            <li>After <strong>six (6) months</strong> of expiration, individuals must start the process for a new license and pay all initial licensing fees. This includes a background check and salesperson test.</li>
            <li>The duplicate license fee is <strong>$5.00</strong> for lost, stolen, or destroyed licenses.</li>
            <li>Transfer fee is <strong>$5.00</strong>. A new salesperson license in the name of the new employer must be obtained before engaging in the activities of a salesperson.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <p class="section-label">Application Steps</p>
    <div class="steps-list mb-4">

        <div class="step-item">
            <div class="step-badge">1</div>
            <p>Complete the Salesperson Licensing Application (<a href="https://transportation.wv.gov/DMV/DMVFormSearch/Salesperson_License_Application.pdf" target="_blank" class="step-link">download form here</a> or obtain a form at any DMV regional office).</p>
        </div>

        <div class="step-item">
            <div class="step-badge">2</div>
            <p>Have the employer sign, date, and check the appropriate box in the certification section at the bottom of the application.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="step-item">
            <div class="step-badge">3</div>
            <p>Complete a background check through digital fingerprinting via <strong>SAFRAN MORPHOTRUST USA</strong> by calling <strong>1-855-766-7746</strong> or visiting <a href="http://www.morphotrust.com/" target="_blank" class="step-link">www.morphotrust.com</a>. All background checks must be submitted to DMV Dealer Services.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="step-item">
            <div class="step-badge">4</div>
            <p>Visit a local DMV Regional Office with your completed application and Morphotrust receipt. Present a valid driver's license or government-issued photo ID.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="step-item">
            <div class="step-badge">5</div>
            <p>Submit a fee of <strong>$7.00</strong> per licensing year. Payment entitles the applicant to one (1) test attempt <strong>(76% correct, or 19 out of 25)</strong>. The test may not be taken more than once per week.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="step-item">
            <div class="step-badge">6</div>
            <p>After passing the test and submitting all required fees and the Morphotrust receipt, the Division will notify the applicant via letter once the background check is approved. <em>Note: The Division will automatically update the temporary license to permanent status in the DMV system — it is not necessary to obtain another Salesperson Identification Card.</em></p>
        </div>

    </div>

    <p class="section-label">Helpful Tools &amp; Forms</p>
    <div class="list-group shadow-sm rounded resource-list mb-4">

        <div class="list-group-item list-group-item-action py-3 px-4">
