                   target="_blank"
                   class="text-decoration-none stretched-link">
                    Salesperson Test Study Guide
                </a>
            </h6>
            <p class="mb-0 small">Study guide to help prepare for the salesperson licensing exam.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="list-group-item list-group-item-action py-3 px-4">
            <h6 class="mb-1 fw-semibold">
                <a href="https://transportation.wv.gov/DMV/DMVFormSearch/Salesperson_License_Application.pdf"
                   target="_blank"
                   class="text-decoration-none stretched-link">
                    Motor Vehicle Salesperson License Application
                </a>
            </h6>
            <p class="mb-0 small">Official application form for a new motor vehicle salesperson license.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="list-group-item list-group-item-action py-3 px-4">
            <h6 class="mb-1 fw-semibold">
                <a href="https://transportation.wv.gov/DMV/DMVFormSearch/ARCHIVE/DMV-12-DS_Salesperson-Notification-of-Change-WF.pdf"
                   target="_blank"
                   class="text-decoration-none stretched-link">
                    Salesperson Notification of Change Form
                </a>
            </h6>
            <p class="mb-0 small">Use this form to report any changes to an existing salesperson license.</p>
        </div>

    </div>

